description: This skill will give the user a set of 5 randomized questions about camping and national parks in the form of a trivia game!  The user asks Alexa to play Camping Triva, and is scored to see how many quesions they can answer correctly out of 5.  The questions are randomly given to the user.
name: Camping Trivia
shortDescription: This Alexa App gives a random set of questions related to camping an parks.
